title: Mahmood ul Haq
text:
Mahmood ul Haq is a Pakistani politician who has been a member of the <a href="Provincial%20Assembly%20of%20the%20Punjab">Provincial Assembly of the Punjab</a> since August 2018.
Political career.
He was elected to the <a href="Provincial%20Assembly%20of%20the%20Punjab">Provincial Assembly of the Punjab</a> as a candidate of <a href="Pakistan%20Muslim%20League%20%28N%29">Pakistan Muslim League (N)</a> from Constituency PP-141 (Sheikhupura-VII) in <a href="2018%20Pakistani%20general%20election">2018 Pakistani general election</a>.
